    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      static class  SciencePlan.STATUS
      This is the enum indicating the status of a science plan COMPLETE = The plan finishes running TESTED = The plan finished testing CANCELLED = The plan has been canceled RUNNING = The plan is being run in OCS SUBMITTED = The plan has been submitted to OCS VALIDATED = The plan has been validated by the science observer INVALIDATED = The plan has been rejected by the science observer The flows can be as follows.
      static class  SciencePlan.TELESCOPELOC
      Location of the two Gemini telescopes, Hawaii = North, Chile = South

      • SciencePlan

        public SciencePlan​(java.lang.String creator,
                   java.lang.String submitter,
                   double fundingInUSD,
                   java.lang.String objectives,
                   StarSystem.CONSTELLATIONS starSystem,
                   java.util.Date startDate,
                   java.util.Date endDate,
                   SciencePlan.TELESCOPELOC telescopeLocation,
                   DataProcRequirement dataProcRequirements)
        A constructor with all the parameters
        Parameters:
        creator - the creator of the science plan
        submitter - the submitter of the science plan
        fundingInUSD - the amount of funding in dollars
        objectives - the objectives of the science plan
        starSystem - the star system to be observed by this science plan
        startDate - the starting date and time of this observation
        endDate - the ending date and time of this observation
        telescopeLocation - the telescope to be used for this observation (the TELESCOPELOC enum, either HAWAII or CHILE)
        dataProcRequirements - the requirements for processing the collected data (i.e., images)
